data.description:
Wonderful home in highly sought after Windsor neighborhood. The INGROUND POOL with a slide is perfect for entertaining family and friends. The master suite features an two walk in closets, an updated bathroom with two vanities and a huge walk in shower. The master also opens to the oversized sunroom. The living room has a beautiful corner fireplace and built in book cases. Utility room is large with storage. The second back yard area features a grilling patio and is perfect for a dog run. The pool was refinished and bathrooms redone in summer 2023. this is a great home ready for your family. 

All updates per seller
